<li class="listenpunkt"><a class="https" href="https://www.darmstaedter-signal.de/" target="_blank" alt="www.darmstaedter-signal.de" title="www.darmstaedter-signal.de">Arbeitskreis Darmst&auml;dter Signal</a> &ndash; Das Forum f&uuml;r kritische Staatsb&uuml;rger in Uniform (<a class="https" href="https://www.facebook.com/darmstaedtersignal" target="_blank" alt="www.facebook.com/darmstaedtersignal" title="www.facebook.com/darmstaedtersignal">Facebook</a>, <a class="https" href="https://twitter.com/DasSignal83" target="_blank" alt="twitter.com/DasSignal83" title="twitter.com/DasSignal83">Twitter</a>, <a class="https" href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darmst&auml;dter_Signal" target="_blank" alt="de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darmst&auml;dter_Signal" title="de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darmst&auml;dter_Signal">Wikipedia</a>)</li>
